1		| board		| Board
player_count	| homes		| Home
player_count	| players	| Player
player_count	| houses	| houses
player_count *4 | figures	| figure
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
initialize()
new()
start()
stop()
continue()
run()
end()
gameOver()





Board
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2-player_count 	| houses 	| type House
1 		| field 	| type Field
2-player_count 	| homes 	| type Home
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
generateBoard()



Figure
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1		| color		| int
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
move()
